profile: S&J Renovations is locally owned and independently operated. Owner/operator Brent Jones has more than 20 years of experience in all aspects of home renovations and project management. He offers both a professional approach and top-notch customer service. Whether it's a kitchen or bathroom renovation, or an entire house you're looking to build, S&J Renovations can transform any room in your home.
